title: 2013–14 AIK IF season
text: The <a href="2013%E2%80%9314%20SHL%20season">2013–14</a> <a href="AIK%20IF">AIK IF</a> <a href="season%20%28sports%29">season</a> was AIK's 30th season in the <a href="Swedish%20Hockey%20League">Swedish Hockey League</a> (formerly known as Elitserien), the top division in Sweden.
